message.entry: The input table contains a nested cell array with an empty element. Writing nested cell arrays containing empty elements to an XML file using writetable is not supported.
The input table contains a nested cell array element. Writing nested cell arrays to an XML file using writetable is not supported.
Writing nested tables is not supported. Use splitvars on the nested table to split multicolumn variables into single-column variables before writing.
The input table contains an unsupported datatype. Supported datatypes include: numerics, characters, strings, categoricals, and time types.
